CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 1, 1954, pg. 17, reads: "Heagy - Spalding Inquest Scenes - Police Witness - Lieut. Paul Duffy, in charge of Centre Avenue Police Station the night Officer William H. Heagy was killed, confers with Detective Robert Butzler (right), who apprehended Spalding after the shooting. - All Photos by Harris."
TitMainTitle: Lieutenant Paul Duffy wearing police uniform, and Detective Robert Butzler, posed in interior at Heagy - Spalding inquest
